sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS Reencrypt
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant API as DS Pipelines API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows Controller
    participant Pod as Pipeline Step Pod
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant S3 as MinIO / S3<br/>9000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: DSPA Reconciliation (Operator deploys components)

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        User->>+API: DSPA CR change triggers reconciliation
        Note right of User: DSPO Controller watches DSPA CRs<br/>via ServiceAccount RBAC
        API->>DB: Health check (3306/TCP MySQL)<br/>Optional TLS, Password auth
        API->>S3: Health check (9000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS)<br/>Optional TLS 1.2+, S3 credentials
        API->>API: Deploy all managed components<br/>via Kubernetes API (6443/TCP HTTPS)
    end

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution (Runtime)

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        User->>+Route: POST /apis/v1beta1/pipelines<br/>HTTPS TLS
        Route->>+KRBP: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
        KRBP->>KRBP: SubjectAccessReview<br/>Check DSPA api subresource permission
        KRBP->>+API: Forward to API server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
        API->>API: Create pipeline run
        API->>+Argo: Create Workflow CR<br/>via K8s API (ServiceAccount RBAC)
        Argo->>+Pod: Execute pipeline step
        Pod->>+MLMD: Log artifact/execution lineage<br/>8080/TCP gRPC, Optional mTLS<br/>Auth: NetworkPolicy
        MLMD-->>-Pod: Lineage recorded
        Pod->>+S3: Upload artifacts<br/>9000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional TLS, S3 credentials
        S3-->>-Pod: Artifact stored
        Pod-->>-Argo: Step complete
        Argo-->>-API: Workflow status update
        PA->>+API: Sync workflow state<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>ServiceAccount auth
        API->>+DB: Persist run state<br/>3306/TCP MySQL<br/>Optional TLS, Password
        DB-->>-API: State persisted
        API-->>-PA: State synced
        API-->>-KRBP: Pipeline result
        KRBP-->>-Route: Response
        Route-->>-User: JSON Response
    end

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Managed Pipeline Import

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note right of User: DSPO Controller fetches<br/>managed pipeline bundles
        API->>+S3: Fetch from OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Registry credentials
        S3-->>-API: Pipeline manifest (managed-pipelines.json)
        Note right of API: init-managed-pipelines container<br/>writes to shared emptyDir volume
        API->>API: API server reads pipelines<br/>from shared volume
    end
